---
// Rule 4 — disclaimer on every page.
//
// Mobile-friendly behavior: 2 lines max on small screens, expandable on tap.
// Sticky on top until first scroll, then remains in the viewport as a thin
// strip. No cookie that hides it permanently.
---

<aside
  id="site-disclaimer"
  class="no-print sticky top-0 z-40 border-b border-disclaimer-border bg-disclaimer-bg text-disclaimer-text"
  role="note"
  aria-label="Site disclaimer"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-2 text-xs leading-snug sm:text-sm">
    <p class="line-clamp-2">
      <span class="font-semibold">Informational only.</span> This site is not legal advice and not a substitute for an
      attorney. We do not draft legal documents.{' '}
      <a href="/disclaimer" class="underline decoration-disclaimer-text">Read the full disclaimer</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</aside>
